_sText: Hello, once more a very well done buzzkill version.. -> The Best and most High Quality one yet ! It was made by audiOtrash, he produced it for our Server / Community, which has a very well frequent visited buzzkill maps only Server. The theme stayed close to the ice look, but got better /custom textures. It has a secret, if you can reach the button on top of the tower in the middel, you can initiate some nice Minimal Techno Music and visual effects ! 2 ways to get on top, a hidden switch and surely by trying to jump up there ! ( u can do it ) The top / outer borders are walkable now, reach them by the jump portals ! (The map was created almost half a year ago..) We hope you like it, some smashing new buzzkill action for you ;-) Visit us : **www.SCHEITERHAUFEN.info - Fun Server Community** **Our Server: ** SCHEITERHAUFEN.info - 84.16.241.54:28500 -> Based on original: 1.6 fy_buzzkill by Plank
